{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1106835, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 217051, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "又有一个懵懂的学生想买pad了sos 希望dy们帮解答一下困惑与犹豫", "timestamp": 1613569487, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1106839, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 217051, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "pros是啥", "timestamp": 1613569492, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1106841, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 217051, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "擦，还以为是两个app", "timestamp": 1613569518, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1106858, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 217051, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有一种练托福口语题在列要点的感觉", "timestamp": 1613569668, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1106862, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 217051, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "pro：用pad看视频，和手机一样方便，比手机屏幕大。\ncon：去图书馆会多背一个pad虽然有的时候并不会用到", "timestamp": 1613569700, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1106867, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 217051, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我没觉得伤视力，毕竟如果没有pad我就用手机或电脑看了...", "timestamp": 1613569747, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1107032, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 217051, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "iPad 多年用户感觉 iPad 看文档并没有很舒服，特别是在桌上的时候放在桌子上的 iPad 完全没有立起来的电脑舒服", "timestamp": 1613571462, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1107036, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 217051, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "iPad 的定位还是躺在沙发里打游戏/追剧，当然便携和记笔记的优势还是没什么争议的", "timestamp": 1613571513, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1107088, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 217051, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 学习是真的方便！上课只带iPad和pencil，大书包换小书包，而且都是电子教材，ppt，上课前也不用再去打印了，直接电子版记笔记。不过毁眼睛也有可能是真的，用了一年，可能是老用黑底白字的原因，度数确实涨高了", "timestamp": 1613571952, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 217051, "reply": 9, "tag": null, "text": "想买pad的pros and cons\npro：\n1 在pad上看长篇资料比电脑上舒服（有种捧在手心的感觉）\n2 看外文查词很方便\n3 可以省掉我买本子（尤其是手账等）和打印的钱\n4 可以不用每天背大部头\ncons：\n1 据说伤视力（希望求证）\n2 dz字写得很丑，估计不会用它做电子笔记\n3 据说打印下来能够更好阅读", "timestamp": 1613569312, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1613571952, "url": "", "vote": {}}}